{"tid":1343603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警諗住英雄式反cup, 點知玩到咁大收唔到科","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T19:27:02.000Z","uid":12404,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"29e32cccfca41b972e7a38de8f1f0f0f588beee2","tid":1343603,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfc3494801403e59f07d781ce303366b7f88486","tid":1343603,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:04:06.000Z","msg":"何君堯開live!!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JuniusHoKwanYiu/videos/407033843250150/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJuniusHoKwanYiu%2Fvideos%2F407033843250150%2F&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=f7bb07d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JuniusHoKwanYiu/videos/407033843250150/</a>"},{"pid":"0ea620ec1fe5ef4ca6c63c10684af8416ec537d9","tid":1343603,"uid":53377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:05:25.000Z","msg":"八鄉分區<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑社會</strong></span></span>指揮官 李漢民<br />\n<br />\n一批身穿白色衫的人士兩次到元朗站內，毆打市民，又向市民掟雜物。部分人更走入車廂打人。至少8人受傷，有人頭部受傷，血流披面。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者問在場警員，為何這麼遲到場。元朗區八鄉分區指揮官李漢民回應，警方是接報到場，至於何時到場，他說<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「睇唔到錶」</span></span>，反問記者有否見到剛才的混亂場面。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有否拘捕人，李漢民說暫時未有。有在場記者問，事發時車廂有很多人，為何無警員在場。李漢民回應稱不要質問他。記者繼續追問，李漢民就回應「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你咁樣係唔會令到我驚」。</span></span>"},{"pid":"210effebdf804009ff52e8cf34d6055b852e26ad","tid":1343603,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:05:28.000Z","msg":"英雄式反CUP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪又係交戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65fa3bd6cb636736c3a7e88ccefed49339ecc73","tid":1343603,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:16:00.000Z","msg":"首先全世界都知佢地做戲 就唔會有英雄式反cup呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後而家老黑有人死左 警犬好似收唔到科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fcf3017fc6021cab2b2c2830052e450c9e8358","tid":1343603,"uid":97451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:17:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7adba31fb9726d52573eade5448427bf4177eaaf","tid":1343603,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:19:09.000Z","msg":"睇得出何妖只係扮風騷<br />\n聽日傳媒媒體文宣一定要收佢皮<br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n「文宣」聽日主題集火黑警連開三十多槍轟爆示威者頭，［撐警］何君堯指使元朗黑社會濫害平民！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1342705\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1342705</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/iDmdy6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiDmdy6F.png&h=3dfdc8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Ye9e22K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYe9e22K.png&h=a683180a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/uMPe22J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMPe22J.gif&h=c571b636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBJbX6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBJbX6.jpg&h=e8ea5f80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c55369aeda66b3c6f127b0ea4941e051d4e0fcd","tid":1343603,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d65fa3bd6cb636736c3a7e88ccefed49339ecc73","tid":1343603,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy